  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Video Editor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Video Editor</strong></p>\n<p>We are looking for a skilled and creative Video Editor to work on long and short formats. The editor should be expected to work with on a variety of projects, transforming footage shot by the production team into compelling visual stories based off the project specs.</p>\n<p><strong>Responsiblities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Take charge of video ideation and creation</li>\n  <li>Able to weave footages to tell a compelling story</li>\n  <li>Implement creative notes from stakeholders and clients.</li>\n  <li>Work closely with team members to understand requirements and communicate the intended creative vision for production.</li>\n  <li>Organised and attentive in the editing and storage for different content</li>\n  <li>Keep up to date with latest video marketing/ social trends</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Qualifications</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Film, Sound &amp; Video or its equivalent.</li>\n  <li>Is a team player</li>\n  <li>Creative, technically inclined</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of editing principles</li>\n  <li>Able to work well under pressure</li>\n  <li>Fast turnaround </li>\n  <li>· Good understanding of social media production</li>\n  <li>Proficient with various video editing tools (Adobe Premiere, Audition, After Effects)</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in other areas (ie, colour grading, VFX) is a plus.</li>\n</ul>",
